The work is now committed to the candour of the Ame- rican public, with the humble hope that it may prove an acceptable offen-ing to' the theological student and the minister of the gospel, and a valuable help to the youth of our country, in the study of a language so highly favum-ed in being made the vehicle of divine inspiration.
